title: Liquor and fuel should not come under GST: Telangana Finance Minister Etela Rajender
dc:creator: PTI
content: Telangana Finance Minister Etela Rajender today said the state would suffer huge financial losses if the Centre brings petrol and diesel under the ambit of Goods and Services Tax (GST).
contentSnippet: Telangana Finance Minister Etela Rajender today said the state would suffer huge financial losses if the Centre brings petrol and diesel under the ambit of Goods and Services Tax (GST).
